---
alwaysApply: false
description: Traces, metrics, and system debugging
globs: got/domain/events/**/*.py
---

**Responsibilities:**
- Log orchestrator decisions
- Capture domain events (CycleDetected, ContradictionDetected, GraphUpdated)
- Expose metrics (graph size, violation count, etc.)
- Support audit and debugging

**Constraints:**
- Read-only; does not modify the graph
- Can be used in production without affecting reasoning

**Dependencies:** got.domain.events, event handlers